
This set of scripts makes a list of users who can access to the observations (PI/observer). 

Dir: /data/mta4/obs_ss/

Scripts:
--------
make_access_list.py

Data:
-----
SyBase access

Output:
-------
<obs_ss>/access_list

Cron job:
---------
c3po-v as mta
6 12,18,23 * * 0-6 cd /data/mta4/obs_ss; /data/mta4/obs_ss/make_access_list.py >> $HOME/Logs/make_access.cron 2>&1 
